{
  "stem": "5654.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we-- we had breakfast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, we [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] decided to tell each other stories, what happened to us, what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told me-- I remember before the war, he came to say goodbye to my mother and to us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he joined the-- the French army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And his story was that he was caught with his-- with his-- unit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was caught by the German and sent to camp in Germany for two years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And being a French soldier, luckily, they didn't touch him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was prisoner of war in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he came back after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he didn't know where we were, whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so that was a most amazing story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said to me, I'd like you to meet-- there is a wedding tonight, one of your cousins.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he took us, first of all, to-- we walked down [INAUDIBLE] to Boulevard [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there, there was a cafe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he introduced me to the owner of the cafe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was my-- another uncle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was my-- my father had a sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was her husband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, of course, we set in the cafe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we talked and so on, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then he took us to another uncle, to another cousin, which we-- of course, today, they must be passed away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that evening, we went to the wedding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were the life of the party, of course, my brother and I.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They couldn't believe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was a fantastic reunion, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They couldn't look after us, because they didn't have the means.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we had to go back to the home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But we saw every now and again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then we moved away from the home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
